en]]\n#[[Ukrainian language|Ukrainian]]\n#[[Urdu]]\n#[[Uyghur language|Uyghur]]\n#[[Uzbek language|Uzbek]]\n#[[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]]\n#[[Welsh language|Welsh]]\n#[[West Frisian language|West Frisian]]\n#[[Xhosa language|Xhosa]]\n#[[Yiddish]]\n#[[Yoruba language|Yoruba]]\n#[[Zulu language|Zulu]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n{{hidden begin|title=History|titlestyle=background:DeepSkyBlue; text-align:center;|style=font-size:100%;}}\n#1st stage <!-- date to be filled in -->\n##English to and from [[French language|French]]\n##English to and from [[German language|German]]\n##English to and from [[Spanish language|Spanish]]\n#2nd stage <!-- date to be filled in -->\n##English to and from [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]\n#3rd stage <!-- date to be filled in -->\n##English to and from [[Italian language|Italian]]\n#4th stage <!-- date to be filled in -->\n##English to and from [[Standard Chinese|Chinese (Simplified)]]\n##English to and from [[Japanese language|Japanese]]\n##English to and from [[Korean language|Korean]]\n#5th stage (launched April 28, 2006)<ref name=\"Statistical machine translation\"/>\n##English to and from [[Arabic]]\n#6th stage (launched December 16, 2006)\n##English to and from [[Russian language|Russian]]\n#7th stage (launched February 9, 2007)\n##English to and from [[Standard Chinese|Chinese (Traditional)]]\n##[[Standard Chinese|Chinese (Simplified to and from Traditional)]]\n#8th stage (all 25 language pairs use Google's machine translation system) (launched October 22, 2007)\n##English to and from [[Dutch language|Dutch]]\n##English to and from [[Greek language|Greek]]\n#9th stage <!-- date to be filled in -->\n##English to and from [[Hindi]]\n#10th stage (as of this stage, translation can be done between any two languages, using English as an intermediate step, if needed) (launched May 8, 2008)\n##[[Bulgarian language|Bulgarian]]\n##[[Croatian language|Croatian]]\n##[[Czech language|Czech]]\n##[[Danish language|Danish]]\n##[[Finnish language